---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
    <div class="bg-gray-950 py-20">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 prose prose-invert">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold">Home Network Security Tips for Families in 2026</h1>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">July 2026 • RigRescue Helpful Tips</p>

            <p>With more devices than ever connected at home, securing your Wi-Fi network is more important than ever. Here are practical steps every family should take.</p>

            <h2>Essential Security Steps</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>I know this goes without saying but use a strong, unique Wi-Fi password</li>
                <li>Enable WPA3 encryption</li>
                <li>Set up guest network for visitors.</li>
                <li>Keep router firmware updated (this is THE most overlooked security risk in home networks today!)</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Need Help?</h2>
            <p>RigRescue can audit your home network, recommend improvements, and set up secure configurations — both remotely and in-person in the Deltona area.</p>

            <div class="text-center mt-12">
                <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 px-10 py-4 rounded-xl text-lg font-medium">
                    Secure Your Home Network
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
